data.text: @MusicMundial @beyoutifulbee_ @MacMiller @ArianaGrande why do we have to make this about her??

@MusicMundial @MacMiller @ArianaGrande Mental health can affect absolutely anyone at sometime or another in their lifetime. The reasons why can be so complicated at times & many hide it from even their loved ones because they feel ashamed. Mac Miller was more open than many, but he sadly lost that fight to his demons
